('Peroni Negroni','[".5 oz    Gin",".5 oz    Italian red bitter liqueur",".5 oz    Sweet Vermouth","1/6 bottle   Peroni lager"]','["STIR gin, Campari and vermouth with ice and fine strain into chilled shot glass. Carefully position the shot glass in the beer glass. Then carefully POUR Peroni into beer glass so not quite reaching the top of the shot glass, being careful not to splash any beer into shot glass. Instruct drinker to drink from beer glass and so inevitably also shot glass. Use sturdy glassware."]','["None"]','["Shot and Beer glass","\n\n\n\n\n\nCocktail glassware\nCocktails are something of a luxury. You don’t just ping a cap and pour – they take a degree of time and skill to...\n"]'),
